{"expireTime":9007200804686247000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-html-daeb3dbb5b8e8b82bf2bb01065817a68-gatsby-remark-graphvizgatsby-remark-code-titlesgatsby-remark-imagesgatsby-remark-responsive-iframegatsby-remark-autolink-headersgatsby-remark-prismjsgatsby-remark-copy-linked-filesgatsby-remark-smartypants-","val":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-root-import\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-root-import\" aria-label=\"gatsby plugin root import permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-root-import</h1>\n<p>Set Webpack to resolve root, allowing you to import modules from an absolute project path rather than relative <code class=\"language-text\">../../</code> paths.</p>\n<p><strong>NOTE:</strong> Plugin has different installation and usage instructions to support both Gatsby V1 and V2.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 id=\"gatsby-v2-instructions\"><a href=\"#gatsby-v2-instructions\" aria-label=\"gatsby v2 instructions permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gatsby V2 Instructions</h2>\n<h3 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Install the <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-root-import</code> plugin:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save-dev gatsby-plugin-root-import</code></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add --dev gatsby-plugin-root-import</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-label=\"usage permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h3>\n<p>Add into <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-root-import'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"default-settings\"><a href=\"#default-settings\" aria-label=\"default settings permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Default Settings</h3>\n<p>Webpack v4 drops <code class=\"language-text\">resolve.root</code> in favor of <code class=\"language-text\">resolve.alias</code> found <a href=\"https://webpack.js.org/configuration/resolve/#resolve-alias\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>If no options are specified, the plugin creates a default alias of <code class=\"language-text\">src</code> to your project <code class=\"language-text\">src</code> folder.</p>\n<p>This means you should be able to import modules like such:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// importing gatsbyProject/src/yourFolder/YourComponent.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> YourComponent <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/yourFolder/YourComponent'</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"plugin-options\"><a href=\"#plugin-options\" aria-label=\"plugin options permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Plugin Options</h3>\n<p>You can pass as many keys as you want into the plugin options, and they will map to Webpackâ€™s <code class=\"language-text\">alias</code> configuration.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">alias</code> takes an object with keys of your alias names, and values of directory strings <a href=\"https://webpack.js.org/configuration/resolve/#resolve-alias\">like so</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'path'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-root-import'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        src<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">join</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        pages<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">join</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/pages'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>This means you should be able to import modules like such:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// from the 'src' alias</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// importing gatsbyProject/src/yourFolder/YourComponent.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> YourComponent <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/yourFolder/YourComponent'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// from the 'pages' alias</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// importing gatsbyProject/src/pages/YourPage.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> YourPage <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'pages/YourPage'</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 id=\"gatsby-v1-instructions\"><a href=\"#gatsby-v1-instructions\" aria-label=\"gatsby v1 instructions permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gatsby V1 Instructions</h2>\n<h3 id=\"install-1\"><a href=\"#install-1\" aria-label=\"install 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Install the <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-root-import</code> plugin:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save-dev --save-exact gatsby-plugin-root-import@1.0.0</code></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add --dev gatsby-plugin-root-import@1.0.0</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"usage-1\"><a href=\"#usage-1\" aria-label=\"usage 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h3>\n<p>Add into <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-root-import'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"default-settings-1\"><a href=\"#default-settings-1\" aria-label=\"default settings 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Default Settings</h3>\n<p>If no options are specified, the plugin defaults to your project root folder.</p>\n<p>This means you should be able to import modules like such:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// importing gatsbyProject/src/yourFolder/YourComponent.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> YourComponent <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/yourFolder/YourComponent'</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"plugin-options-1\"><a href=\"#plugin-options-1\" aria-label=\"plugin options 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Plugin Options</h3>\n<p>You can pass a <code class=\"language-text\">root</code> option. You can specify your own folder, such as <code class=\"language-text\">src</code>.\nThis option corresponds with Webpack v3â€™s <code class=\"language-text\">resolve.root</code> found <a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/docs/wiki/configuration#resolveroot\">here</a>.\nThis may be both a directory string, or an array of directory strings.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'path'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-root-import'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        root<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">join</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>This means you can import modules with projectâ€™s <code class=\"language-text\">src</code> folder as <code class=\"language-text\">root</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// importing gatsbyProject/src/yourFolder/YourComponent.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> YourComponent <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'yourFolder/YourComponent'</span></code></pre></div>"}